    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Uncertainty quantification over key boundary condition inputs demonstrates that NIH predictions remain below the RH < 1 acceptance threshold across the 95th-percentile uncertainty envelope. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
